lead_paragraph: A jury today convicted a young woman of conspiring with two boys to murder her twin sister, who foiled the attack with a quick call to the police. Jeen Han, 23, wept as the lengthy verdict against her was read in Orange County Superior Court. Her twin sister, Sunny Han, was not present.
abstract: Orange County, Calif, jury convicts Jeen Han of conspiring with two boys to murder her twin sister Sunny Han, who foiled attack by calling police; convicts codefendants Archie Bryant, 17, and John Sayarath, 16, of conspiracy (S)

headline.main: Woman Guilty of Trying to Kill Her Twin
